    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "forget the numbers, they won't help. there's no one left out here. everything is just grey and cold. i've tried so hard to keep us going, but look at us. we're just waiting to die in the dirt anyway. it feels like it's just time to stop, doesnt it?",
